GeoScaler Attribute Modifier Plug-in
====================================

The GeoScaler Attribute Modifier Plug-in (AMP) scales a piece of geometry by a
factor that the user can specify. If the location being modified doesn't
contain any geometry data, an error location will be added to the scene graph.

Environment Variables
---------------------

KATANA_HOME  The Katana installation directory at compile-time

Building
--------

1. Ensure the environment variables listed above have been set.
2. Run 'make'.
3. Copy 'out/GeoScaler.so' to the 'Libs' subdirectory within a Katana
   resources path.
